code: export function usersFetchDataSuccess(users){return{type:"USERS_FETCH_DATA_SUCCESS",users:users};}export function usersFetchData(url){return function(dispatch){fetch(url).then(function(response){if(!response.ok){throw new Error(response.statusText);}return response;}).then(function(response){return response.json();}).then(function(persons){return dispatch(usersFetchDataSuccess(persons));}).catch(function(){});};}
